    <!-- Application Structure Plan: The SPA uses a thematic, single-page scrolling design with a top navigation bar for quick access. The core is an interactive vertical timeline for work history, where clicking an item reveals details in a separate panel. This encourages exploration. A dashboard section with charts highlights key quantitative achievements upfront for immediate impact. Skills are visualized with a radar chart for a quick overview. This structure transforms the static CV into an engaging professional narrative, prioritizing user interaction and data visualization over a simple linear document. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: Work History -> Goal: Show Progression -> Viz: Interactive Vertical Timeline -> Interaction: Click to show details -> Justification: More engaging and less cluttered than a list; Method: HTML/CSS + JS. | Key Metrics (Followers, Votes) -> Goal: Compare/Show Proportion -> Viz: Bar Chart, Donut Chart -> Interaction: Hover tooltips -> Justification: Instantly communicates quantifiable success; Library: Chart.js. | Skills -> Goal: Organize/Summarize -> Viz: Radar Chart -> Interaction: Hover tooltips -> Justification: Provides a quick visual summary of skill balance; Library: Chart.js. -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
